# Raw archive blobs (design D3): the local working copy of every fetched
# source lives under archive/, but only archive-manifest.json (repo root)
# is versioned. R2 is the canonical archived_url for every source once
# credentials are configured; keeping blobs out of git keeps clones fast.
/archive/**
!/archive/.gitkeep
.vercel
.gstack/
